Name: Feixiao
Desc: The Xianzhou Yaoqing's Merlin's Claw and one of the Seven Arbiter-Generals. Unconventional and straightforward, she exudes effortless charm.\nShe is skilled in all forms of martial arts and has honed herself into a supreme weapon. She is widely adored by Xianzhou soldiers and civilians alike as "The Vanquishing General."\nHowever, she bears the burden of the Moon Rage affliction. If she were to hunt down all the abominations in her limited lifetime â€” then the only enemy Feixiao has would be herself.

1.Desc: After launching "Boltsunder Blitz" or "Waraxe Skyward," additionally increases the Ultimate DMG dealt by Feixiao by an amount equal to <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak> of the original DMG, stacking up to <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> time(s) and lasting until the end of the Ultimate action.

2.Desc: In the Talent's effect, for every 1 instance of follow-up attack launched by ally targets, Feixiao gains 1 point of "Flying Aureus." This effect can trigger up to <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> time(s) per turn.

3.Desc: Ultimate Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>.\nBasic ATK Lv. +1, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>10</unbreak>.

5.Desc: Skill Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>.\nTalent Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>.

During this time, can ignore Weakness Type to reduce the target's Toughness. When the target is not <u>Weakness Broken</u>, Feixiao's Weakness Break Efficiency increases by <unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak>.\nDuring the attack, Feixiao first launches "Boltsunder Blitz" or "Waraxe Skyward" on the target, for a total of <unbreak>#3[i]</unbreak> time(s).\nAt the end, deals Wind DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of Feixiao's ATK to the target.

122004.Name: Thunderhunt
122004.Desc: Can activate Ultimate when "Flying Aureus" reaches <unbreak>#3[i]</unbreak> points, accumulating up to <unbreak>#4[i]</unbreak> points. Feixiao gains 1 point of "Flying Aureus" for every <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> attacks by ally targets. Feixiao's Ultimate attacks do not count towards this number.\nAfter Feixiao's teammates attack enemy targets, Feixiao immediately launches <u>follow-up attack</u> against the primary target, dealing Wind DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of Feixiao's ATK. This effect can only trigger once per turn and the trigger count resets at the start of Feixiao's turn. When using this attack, increases DMG dealt by this unit by <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#5[i]%</unbreak></color>, lasting for <unbreak>#6[i]</unbreak> turn(s).

While in "Onrush," pulls in enemies within a certain range, and increases this unit's movement speed by <unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak>. After entering battle, gains <unbreak>#4[i]</unbreak> point(s) of "Flying Aureus."\nWhile in "Onrush," actively attacking will start battle with all pulled enemies. After entering battle, deals Wind DMG equal to <unbreak>#3[i]%</unbreak> of Feixiao's ATK to all enemies at the start of each wave. This DMG is guaranteed to CRIT. If more than 1 enemy is pulled in, increases the multiplier of this DMG by <unbreak>#5[i]%</unbreak> for each additional enemy pulled in, up to a maximum of <unbreak>#6[i]%</unbreak>.
